plyTime":"2017-04-30T20:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://www.demilked.com/magazine/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/photography-shutter-speed-aperture-iso-cheat-sheet-chart-fotoblog-hamburg-daniel-peters-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.demilked.com%2Fmagazine%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F04%2Fphotography-shutter-speed-aperture-iso-cheat-sheet-chart-fotoblog-hamburg-daniel-peters-11.jpg&h=2486f216&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我一開始學影相見到呢張圖就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇左幾十個網都仲係一舊雲<br />\n一睇呢張就明撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e8053199dd70f390a6a076874db3497db4867c","tid":223470,"uid":17245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:42:47.000Z","msg":"影相唔好過份依賴相機性能<br />\n而忽略左構圖 主題 有冇野想表達<br />\n<br />\n見香港好多人太依賴相機 鏡頭<br />\n一味大光圈 追求淺景深<br />\n鏡頭一味追要銳利界手<br />\n如果d相好悶 張張都差唔多咁"},{"pid":"b1d2a7f84f79bd35ea6dffa2a81ce45166f8893e","tid":223470,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T16:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩買左部xt10 想認真學下攝影<br />\n上網睇左好多教學講iso 光圈 快門個啲咁<br />\n但睇完都仲係一頭霧水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下邊到有啲詳細啲既教學？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網個d已經係好撚簡單既皮毛野<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔明會唔會係你自己既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0f2d6390fae24c31b3942f2f003d524483f562","tid":223470,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://www.demilked.com/magazine/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/photography-shutter-speed-aperture-iso-cheat-sheet-chart-fotoblog-hamburg-daniel-peters-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.demilked.com%2Fmagazine%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F04%2Fphotography-shutter-speed-aperture-iso-cheat-sheet-chart-fotoblog-hamburg-daniel-peters-11.jpg&h=2486f216&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我一開始學影相見到呢張圖就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇左幾十個網都仲係一舊雲<br />\n一睇呢張就明撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbtw 通常f/5.6-f/8先係最佳光圈<br />\n一般情況都唔洗收光圈收到細過f/11"},{"pid":"13f7c92b83eb20875253e4c9b53ec0635bab9233","tid":223470,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影相唔好過份依賴相機性能<br />\n而忽略左構圖 主題 有冇野想表達<br />\n<br />\n見香港好多人太依賴相機 鏡頭<br />\n一味大光圈 追求淺景深<br />\n鏡頭一味追要銳利界手<br />\n如果d相好悶 張張都差唔多咁</blockquote><br />\n正解 不過樓主乜都唔識 至少都要識set機先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb36d23cc80567bbfe232cf0afb8c96e9061e15","tid":223470,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:17:52.000Z","msg":"想學+1 有部單反但的唔起心肝出去影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Btw初學應唔應該用內置mode? 光圈先決快門先決嗰啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錯得好離譜嘅話屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"17ea209a117ed9d5f994c232b2f91d9acdde2dce","tid":223470,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影相唔好過份依賴相機性能<br />\n而忽略左構圖 主題 有冇野想表達<br />\n<br />\n見香港好多人太依賴相機 鏡頭<br />\n一味大光圈 追求淺景深<br />\n鏡頭一味追要銳利界手<br />\n如果d相好悶 張張都差唔多咁</blockquote><br />\n有無大作睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84dc4ad7e47a2fc31a615454fd0c8c188fca972a","tid":223470,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T19:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學+1 有部單反但的唔起心肝出去影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Btw初學應唔應該用內置mode? 光圈先決快門先決嗰啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錯得好離譜嘅話屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以先影熟所有mode，唔同題材唔同mode, 長曝多數用M mode, 熟左長曝之後大部分題材都識影，之後想影出咩感覺嘅相就用咩mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n睇多d人地影嘅相都好有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}